Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to discuss today?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, who's going to be number uno?\NNumero uno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hippity hop, hi.\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say thank you.\NThank you for saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.\NWhat do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sign that?\NIt's hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:01:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could speak briefly about what the significance is of Lucifer,\Nin particular as related from theosophy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that there are some interpretations that the fall or descent was actually a beneficial thing.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a theory.\NI doubt it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he know it's beneficial?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm asking.\NYeah, I've never come across that interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's the fall, we should thank Lucifer for our fall.\NFor his fall, for sacrificing his place in heaven, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For us?\NEvidently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he wouldn't be Lucifer, would he?\NI guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.\NIf he sacrificed himself for us, he'd be Saint Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NHi, Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.\NWe have some little gifts for your animals and for you guys, some chocolates and some
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,doggie bones.\NYou mentioned in the beginning that you had a bird, a dog, and three cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.\NHere we got bird treats, cat toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know the size of the dog, so we just got these bones.\NBroccoli for broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you have broccoli, we got you broccoli.\NOh, that's for broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how nice.\NShe loves it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?\NAnd we know you love chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We love chocolate.\NBut we didn't know what kind, so we got you from hazelnut to white to dark to coconut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gracious me.\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And a pen to write more books.\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And a pen for each direct book.\NA lioness for Susan and a little cute piggy for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NTo write those books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NBut we don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI was just wondering if you could bless this for me and if I could just shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do both at the same time.\NI'll do both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless this lovely necklace.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThat's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And could you bless my children?\NI have four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lindsay, Brittany, Joshua, and Jessica.\NHow about your new car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to bless that?\NHold them in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, we ask for blessings on that.\NThe beloveds that are being held in our mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NAnd I just wanted to see you both again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to see.\NYour eyes are like blue diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you so much.\NI love both of you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NAnd through the grace of God, through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for you, I'd still be sticking needles in my arms.\NI'd still be living on the street and going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of you, I have a new life.\NAnd I just, I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.\NThank you and God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the reason for addiction.\NAlcohol or drugs, is that, you remember that scale of consciousness goes from the highest to the lowest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the drug or the alcohol suppresses all the lower levels of consciousness.\NAnd therefore, it allows only, you experience only the higher ones because the lower ones have been suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's not coming from the drug.\NIt's just that that's the way you would be in a more advanced state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what the drug does is suppress negative feelings.\NAnd it allows you to feel elation and happiness and joy, which is what you should be experiencing all the time anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is through spiritual endeavor, you reach those higher states of consciousness without the aid, without having to suppress or depress the lower feelings.\NThat's the purpose of the 12 steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of resentments, live one day at a time, and stay with the group spiritual energy.\NI want to say thanks, first of all, so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NAnd my question is, I'm still having a really hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked about it so much in previous lectures, but integrating spirituality with, like, work and stuff.\NI still, I don't know, it probably just takes time, but, like, I really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know if I understand, but I appreciate the profundity of the lectures and everything.\NBut I still have, like, a desire for, like, lots of money and stuff like that that I can't seem to shake off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of money?\NWell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so much that, but just, like, I don't know.\NSuccess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just, like, success, sort of, in material.\NOh, I was going to give you lots of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NI'll tell you, I used to live on Millionaire's Row, and those people shot themselves with the same frequency as people in the poverty section of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.\NSo happiness, then, has nothing to do with material possessions, because even if it was material possessions, what you're experiencing is the joy of accomplishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which is non-material.\NIt's non-physical, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I might get a picture, too.\NOf course, if you've got a lot of money, you can't live in subsidized housing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a student, the county had subsidized housing.\NI lived there for $15 a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bedrooms, $15 a month.\NCan't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was on the GI Bill.\NOh, you signed that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, first, I just wanted to express my gratitude.\NThat you elect to stay here and be our teacher and guide and to your support staff who makes all this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if I could hold someone in my mind, if you could tell me if they are an accurate muscle tester.\NIf they can accurately...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a muscle test to see if the person you're holding in town is a muscle tester.\NI don't know how accurate it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think so?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ask the arm.\NIs what she's asking possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you got the person in mind?\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NWe have permission to ask about the person she's holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is an adequate muscle tester.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they get...\NGo take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes when you first start out doing muscle testing, you sometimes get higher figures than what you should.\NDo you think that my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first start out...\NWhen you first start out doing the muscle testing, you sometimes get a little bit higher calibration or figure than what you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's easy to do because you want the best for everybody.\NSo, it's a common thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, sometimes you're not right on.\NBut could I be the weak link in this test because I'm holding them in mind and I might not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you might be.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never done that before, so...\NYeah, I didn't know if that was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible to test them out.\NYeah, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The testing technique itself, you know, we'd have to do a whole lecture on that again sometime.\NIt's very, very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet people screw it up.\NI don't know how they screw it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's so simple.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we take a picture?\NOh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that purity...\NPeople can't resist putting their intention on a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's rare that people can just be objective.\NAnd what they want, they want a certain answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they're trying to prove that that answer is true because they want it.\NSo, to be detached has to be scientific.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not sure I...\NScientific detachment means you don't care how many molecules there is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the computer figure it out.\NWhatever it is, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you've got to be detached like that.\NI find most people are not that detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the reason they're asking the question to begin with is because they're not detached.\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense.\NThey say, this stock is going to go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason they want to know that is because they own a bunch of it.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you.\NMy question is, I'm having a lot of trouble letting go of my judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgmentalism and my spiritual ego.\NLetting go of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgmentalism.\NOh, judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging of everything and it's constant commentary going on all the time and I don't know how to let it go.\NWell, the thing to do is let go of it from your perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, what you don't think is correct or right or something maybe just right for the other person.\NSo, there's no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way of knowing.\NWell, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You see somebody angry and expressive and now you think they're wrong.\NWell, that person spent three years in psychoanalysis learning how to be aggressive and assertive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the first time I told somebody to F off and gave them the arm.\NI was jubilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them off.\NI told them where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:12:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them where to go.\NI was happy as a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy as a lamb.\NI was wondering if you could sign my course book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cookbook?\NMy spiritual cookbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NThat's a neat cover you have on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember the first time I gave somebody the finger.\NI was just jubilant that I was so assertive and aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.\NBefore that, I was always afraid of offending somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?\NI didn't want to breathe in and out for fear I would offend somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, this is a book you must read.\NLook at his tatters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my picture.\NIf you could sign that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign that.\NOh, goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good...\NOh, he has a white sharpie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good looking guy.\NWho is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My question was about, are you familiar with the Self-Realization Fellowship?\NAnd if so, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about their lessons?\NWhat's the Self-Realization Fellowship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, you're not familiar with them.\NNo, it's a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yucca Nauticus.\NYucca Nauticus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yucca Nauticus.\NYou wrote the autobiography?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not familiar with it as an organization.\NYou're asking me about an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Self-Realization Fellowship organization is what you're asking me about.\NYes, I think the last time I went near that, it's in the high 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-Realization 500 is over 580, 575.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,570.\NSelf-Realization Fellowship is over 565.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NIt's in the high 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,565.\NWhat about Yogananda's teachings himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?\NThe founder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yogananda.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yogananda's teachings itself.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the list up there.\NHe's like 570, 575, 580, 590, 585.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Supercalifragilisticexpialidocious.\NPretty high then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time.\NI appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nice meeting you.\NOh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Autobiography of a yogi it's what he's asking me about.\NYes, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Been so many years, I forgot it.\NHow long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NDr. Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you that I love you very much and I'm really happy to be here.\NThank you, Susan, for sharing the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had something similar happened to me.\NI was lying in bed and I was waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This light came.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know what happened?\Nit was like coming from within me and it came up and it just lit out the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,room yes and it was like I felt like I couldn't breathe that's it and I didn't\Nknow if that was the self like the big self you didn't know if it was what well
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't the small one was it but just you sharing your experience yes that's\Nthe experience of the presence of God itself with a capital S okay thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,very much could I just touch your hand yes thank you well all day I was very\Nteary and just like I felt like I couldn't function I was just crying a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,lot but I was happy yeah and nothing has come close since like absolutely\Nnothing about ten seconds that was it and just you sharing that just brought
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it up within me today so fine yeah I'm getting an echo here it's hard to hear\Nthe person speaking
