Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.96,1:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,oh okay\Nbecause there is no personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.28,1:10:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience salvation or the lack thereof\Nthere is no personal self according to the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.62,1:10:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand\Nyes
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.78,1:10:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so what is there to save\Nif there is no personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.99,1:10:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,who and what is going to be saved\NI know I understand that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.99,1:10:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,okay\Nnow my question
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.99,1:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so the Buddha is enlightenment\Nbecause he went beyond that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.99,1:11:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha is enlightenment\NJesus Christ deals with people who are not enlightened
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.02,1:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,still think they see themselves as sinners\Nand prone to error etc
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.02,1:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that\Nand their need is more for
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.02,1:11:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and their need is more forgiveness\Nand after forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.18,1:11:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they could then come back\Nand do a post-grad course in enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.21,1:11:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,okay\NI get it now
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.21,1:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now\Nnow is my personal question
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.21,1:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born and raised in a Catholic\Nand after
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.21,1:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,even I got married\Nmy first marriage in Catholic Church
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.21,1:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,later on in my life\Nlater later on in my life
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.21,1:11:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I went away from the Catholic Church\Nbecause there were some questions
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.21,1:11:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and things that I never got answered\Nin my inside
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.21,1:11:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but Jesus Christ was always in my heart\NI found a guru
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.21,1:11:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,later on this new path in my life\Nand that became
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.01,1:11:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it became a lot of\Nenlightenment you would say
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.01,1:12:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of new information for me\Nand a new way of seeing the world
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.01,1:12:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,very wonderful new way\Nof seeing God within me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.01,1:12:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of going\NGod out there
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.01,1:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am so guilty\Nyes
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.01,1:12:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so that was a big difference in my life\Noh yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.01,1:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a way\NJesus was always in my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.17,1:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,yes\NI want to know and ask you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.17,1:12:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,if I should\Nif I hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.17,1:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,this guru\Nand if you could tell me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.17,1:12:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,if I should follow this guru\Nstill
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.17,1:12:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or if I should keep\Nmy heart with Jesus
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.17,1:12:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not in the Catholic Church anyway\Nif I were you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.17,1:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would keep my heart with Jesus\Nbecause Jesus Christ calibrates at a thousand
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.17,1:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and your guru\NI doubt calibrates at a thousand
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.03,1:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or more\Nyou wouldn't be asking me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.03,1:12:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're asking me\Nit would have been resolved already
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.03,1:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah\Nthe spiritual truth of what one is
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.12,1:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is obvious to one who\Nnever mind
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.12,1:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what should I ask further about it\Nthe pathway she's on is sufficient
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.31,1:13:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the pathway you're on is sufficient\Nresist
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.31,1:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah don't be greedy\Nspiritually greedy
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.31,1:13:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you got Jesus Christ\Nand Buddha
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.31,1:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you got gurus\Nand you want to jam me in the box too
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.31,1:13:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you are in the box\Nthat's you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.31,1:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have jammed you in that box too\Nam I too greedy
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.31,1:13:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you think I'm\Nyou think I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.54,1:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,wait\Ncan one be too greedy
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.54,1:13:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in the spiritual path\Nsee
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.54,1:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,your intention\Nand your alignment
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.54,1:13:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is what counts\Nyou see
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.54,1:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,my intention is to be\Non the enlightenment path
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.54,1:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nif Christ is in your heart
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.54,1:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that's already\Nin the enlightened state
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.54,1:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who but an enlightened person\Nwould ask for Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.54,1:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to be in their heart\Nand
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.54,1:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nand
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.54,1:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nand
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.82,1:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nyou understand
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.82,1:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so\Nenlightenment is really a progressive
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.95,1:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,realization of advanced\Nspiritual truth
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.95,1:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual truth eventually becomes\Nnon-communicable
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.95,1:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing that teach\Nbecause it's wordless
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.95,1:14:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so words are useful\Nfor a period of time
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.97,1:14:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,then you go beyond words\Nbecause you become what the words
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.97,1:14:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,are talking about\Nright
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.97,1:14:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nbut you're in that box
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.69,1:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't\Nno
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.69,1:14:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to give up, honey, because you have stopped killing animals already, you know what I'm saying?\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.97,1:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.09,1:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.91,1:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.67,1:14:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.25,1:14:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.27,1:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the first question is a friend of mine is wondering if there are any blocks or gates between level 540 and 570.\NThere aren't any major gates that I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.42,1:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there some?\NThe love becomes more and more unconditional, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.26,1:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the miraculous becomes more and more frequent.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.70,1:15:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.\NAnd then the second question I'm asking for my mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.74,1:15:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm only supposed to ask one per person, but this is just for her.\NSo there's one each.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.71,1:15:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us live with a grandma that's committed to negativity.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.39,1:15:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And both of us are indecisive.\NWe're interested in spiritual evolutions.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.19,1:15:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're wondering how to not allow that to hinder us.\NWell, she can't hinder you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.06,1:15:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But your response to her, what do you think it should be?\NCompassion to her innocence, my response should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.82,1:15:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she's innocent and ignorant, yes.\NSo that's pretty much it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.35,1:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.27,1:15:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you try to be as compassionate and patient as you can be.\NA person like that who has no interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.51,1:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No interest in transcending their own level of consciousness.\NIt's just a matter of learning how to live with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.56,1:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I always think the only way I can think of is by example.\NBut generally, people like that are immune to example too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.65,1:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be kind to you and you can be kind to them and they'll be just as bitchy as usual.\NI'll try my best, but thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.78,1:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult.\NI wouldn't expect any change.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.04,1:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.61,1:16:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get a picture?\NSure as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.81,1:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NWe love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.97,1:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NGet her to smoke marijuana.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.99,1:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That would help.\NTake you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.08,1:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an old lady, 70 years old, and she grew marijuana.\NShe smoked a little marijuana every night before bed for 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.97,1:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She grew it in the kitchen window.\NI said, why do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.51,1:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, because I feel so relaxed and I just go to sleep.\NI said, oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.99,1:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't take off her clothes and go dancing in the village square.\NShe just went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.90,1:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, the reason I and my husband and sister are here is because we needed your\Naura patch, you might say, for our aura so that when we get to higher levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.92,1:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we can go through the high pass.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.80,1:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, when each level of consciousness has its own set of limitations that need to\Nbe transcended, are there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.46,1:17:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?\NAre there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.64,1:17:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?\NAre there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.76,1:17:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?\NAre there limitations?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.18,1:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there limitations?\NThat need to be transcended in the high 500s, 575, 585, are there limitations of perspective
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.38,1:18:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that need to be transcended?\NI don't know if that languaging is directly clinically correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.02,1:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In the high 500s, life becomes increasingly blissful and harmonious and eventually, eventually\Nconstant joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.04,1:18:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the very highest 500s, you go into a state of ecstasy.\NAlso, it's very hard to function in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.08,1:18:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember in the high 500s, if you even looked at love, you couldn't handle it.\NYou'd just get overwhelmed with how profound it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.64,1:18:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And you would find yourself weeping with happiness.\NThat's also noticed in certain...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.02,1:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In religious communities, what do you call them, communities?\NCloistered communities.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.68,1:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloistered, yes.\NThere's a period where you cry all the time, it may last a couple of years, and any time
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.12,1:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you look at something, you can see the love and the beauty inherit.\NSo it sort of melts into the 600 level, and the enlightenment level?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.18,1:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say so, yes.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.18,1:19:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It just sort of melts and blends in.\NIt's a continuity, and of course, demarcating numbers is just an arbitrary, you know, what
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.42,1:19:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature out is it when you can say it's cold, you know, 26 degrees, 25 degrees, 24\Ndegrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.68,1:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that exact, but the higher states of the 500s are increasingly joyful, and as\NI remember, actually ecstatic, and goes into a state of supreme ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.07,1:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of God.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.46,1:20:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of God as profound joy and ecstasy, and you can't function in that state.\NSo you sit on the porch swing all day long.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.42,1:20:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NYou sit on the porch swing all day long.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.42,1:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sit on the porch swing all day long.\NYes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.42,1:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't you bliss.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.74,1:20:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramakrishna went into that state.\NI remember exactly that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.74,1:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.24,1:20:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.36,1:20:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.36,1:20:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.80,1:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.80,1:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.04,1:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.04,1:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question.\NI have a question for my wife who was supposed to be here today but she couldn't make it,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.48,1:20:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll read her question.\NIn May of 2007 my sister died of cancer.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.88,1:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The evening she died, I was swimming, lapsed in the pool, and for a split second I had\Na feeling of extreme ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.74,1:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought my sister just got better, or she died.\NLater, the next day, I found out that the feeling of ecstasy happened at the exact same
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.41,1:21:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,moment my sister died. Yes. Can you tell me the significance of that experience?\NWhat was the relationship between the two people? They were siblings. Siblings, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.12,1:21:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Very close. Yes, well because of the alignment of consciousness she\Nexperienced the ecstasy as you enter heaven, yes. So was it her sister's soul
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.78,1:21:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way, saying goodbye or saying everything is fine? Her sister was\Nmerely experiencing what you experience in that transition from physicality to
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.73,1:21:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,heavenly. Because she was psychically attuned, she vicariously experienced it.\NIt wasn't like transmitted. It's like because of the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.97,1:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,identification between the two. Okay, so my wife's feeling was the same as her\Nsister's feeling at that moment? Yes, yes, yes. She picks up the vibration of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.39,1:22:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yeah. Thank you. Can I shake your hand?\NYes, because as you leave the body and enter that state there's a sense of
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.18,1:22:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstasy. For one thing you've just left pain and suffering and you feel free and\Nyou realize that you're reborn into a new realm. Yes. And it's the state is
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.31,1:22:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstatic. Okay, thank you. I remember in my own lifetime when my\Nmother left the body the state was ecstatic joy. Yeah. Hello Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.51,1:23:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask about surrender letting go of resisting the negative emotions\Nthat come up for me right now a big one is just desire keeps coming up how do I
