Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.05,1:24:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it all right so there's an energy behind the feeling let go resisting that energy\Nin that feeling let yourself crave you don't crave enough lay on the carpet and
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.11,1:24:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,cry and sob that you don't have if you don't have it you won't be able to live\Netc so instead of
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.18,1:24:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,resisting it you're prolonging it it might be better to just surrender to the\Nfeeling and let the feeling run itself out all feelings have a certain
