Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.62,1:26:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah you've moved to a higher level you move to a higher level on that higher level you're not\Ncraving anything you're not craving anything but if you have to give back so you have to give back
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.72,1:26:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to the community or give back and whether it's volunteer or financially or whatever yeah you\Nhave to give something back for what you have and i find that takes you to a different level
